text: Maurice Kennedy (born 16 October 1988) is a Fijian rugby league footballer who plays for the Mount Pritchard Mounties in the NSW Cup. He plays as a scrum half or stand off. Kennedy is a Fijian international. Kennedy’s twin brother John Kennedy also plays for the Mounties and the pair have previously been in the system of the St. George Illawarra Dragons and have also played first grade rugby union. ==References== ==External links== *(archived by web.archive.org) NRL profile *(archived by web.archive.org) NSWRL profile *Zero Tackle profile *(archived by web.archive.org) PNG v Fiji Category:1988 births Category:Fiji national rugby league team players Category:Fijian rugby league players Category:Fijian rugby union players Category:Living people Category:Redcliffe Dolphins players Category:Rugby league five-eighths Category:Rugby league halfbacks Category:Windsor Wolves players
